CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 22, 1939, pg. 8, reads: "Frogs and Friends Make Merry at Post-Lenten Party at Loendi Club - The famous Frogs Club of Pittsburgh were hosts at a gay party last Wednesday night. These scenes were snapped as the group made merry....Right: Mrs. Wilbur Douglass, Mrs. Arthur Powell, Mrs. James Stevenson, Dr. William Cuthbert, Mrs. George Teaman and Mrs. Homer S. Brown. - Photos by Teenie Harris."
TitMainTitle: Women and men playing cards, from left: Kathleen Douglass, Mrs. Arthur Powell, Mrs. James Stevenson, Dr. William Cuthbert, Mrs. George Teaman, and Wilhelmina Byrd Brown, at FROGS party, Loendi Club
